### Add SessionProvider to App Component

Source: https://github.com/posthog/posthog.com/blob/master/contents/tutorials/nextjs-pages-analytics.md

Wraps the entire application with `SessionProvider` from `next-auth/react`. This makes the session data and authentication functions available throughout the Next.js application.

