### PostHog Provider with Bootstrap Data - JavaScript

Source: https://github.com/posthog/posthog.com/blob/master/contents/tutorials/nextjs-ab-tests.md

Initializes the `posthog-js` library with bootstrap data received from the server. This ensures feature flags are available immediately upon client-side load, using `PostHogProvider` for context.

